{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 10 provides further evidence that this result extends also to more challenging neuroevolution tasks.",
    "In summary, this highlights the potential for text-based LLMs to potentially distill teacher algorithms.",
    "One promising future direction may want to explore tuning the tokenizer vocabulary to better accommodate the representation of floating point numbers.",
    "We outline a prompt strategy that enables purely texttrained LLMs to robustly act as an ES on various BBO tasks.",
    "Furthermore, we provide several ablations highlighting the importance of careful solution representation and context construction."
  ]
